Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Located just steps from Pearl, Oxbow is at the heart of the
revitalized Broadway corridor and its burgeoning business
district.

Designed by Don McDonald in association with Kirksey Architecture,
Oxbow offers premier office space and ground-floor retail, restaurants, and beautifully designed public spaces that will enhance the experience for employees, shoppers, diners, and guests.

The project boasts a solar array capable of generating a megawatt
of power, a highly efficient building envelope, an extensive rainwater
collection system, and a progressive geothermal/variable refrigerant
heating and cooling system. The cumulative result is an incredibly
sustainable building that is slated to be Platinum LEED-certified.

Diverse residential options, acclaimed restaurants, unique shops, the award-winning Hotel Emma, and the northern reach of the San Antonio River are all within a leisurely stroll.
